  "base_path": "/hgv-levy",
  "content_id": "dd71b42a-93f6-4afd-88f5-340788abb8d8",
  "description": "Register for the HGV levy and pre-pay your levy",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>You need to pay the <abbr title=\"heavy goods vehicle\">HGV</abbr> levy before entering the UK if the <abbr title=\"heavy goods vehicle\">HGV</abbr>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>is not registered in the UK</li>\n  <li>weighs 12,000kg or more</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You do not have to sign up for an account to use this service, but if you do you can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>pay the <abbr title=\"heavy goods vehicle\">HGV</abbr> levy faster</li>\n  <li>change the dates you want the levy to start (up until 1 day before)</li>\n  <li>get a refund</li>\n  <li>buy a levy for more than 1 month</li>\n  <li>see your payment history</li>\n  <li>register and manage your vehicles</li>\n  <li>allow someone else to manage your account</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You can also check if you’ve paid a levy on your <abbr title=\"heavy goods vehicle\">HGV</abbr>. You’ll need to know the front licence plate number of the vehicle you want to check.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-pay\">How to pay</h2>\n\n<p>You can pay by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>credit or debit card</li>\n  <li>fuel card</li>\n  <li>prepayment through your account</li>\n  <li>bank transfer</li>\n  <li>PayPal</li>\n</ul>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p>You can also pay the <abbr title=\"heavy goods vehicle\">HGV</abbr> levy by phone.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>HGV levy call centre<br>\nTelephone: +44 33 0101 3725<br>\nEvery day, 6am to 6pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://www.hgvlevy.service.gov.uk",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "will_continue_on": "the HGV levy service"
  },
